reviewText: I see that Julianne Buescher is not in this movie. I believe Kevin Carlson is playing Bobby.

Our kids have loved watching this and the few other GeoKids videos for years.  The three main characters (Sunny, Bobby, and Uncle Balzak) are entertaining personalities fun to watch all on their own.  Then add some great songs, and the depth of information and quality animal video footage you would expect from National Geographic, and you have a combination you can't beat.  Fun!
